Title: Valle de San Fernanda (8)
Description.note: Canyon (Freemont Pass) East Side 1926. Description on Image Back: Picture near Old Cemetery between the divide and Newhall. The place where Capt. Pedro Montemegro met Gen. Fremont. A letter was delivered by order of Gen. Andres Pico. The hill was where an American soldier was on the lookout. At the foot of the grade was where Fremont pitched his tent Sept. p. 1847.
